### ===========================
### BOOK API TESTS
### ===========================

### 1. Create a new Book
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Atomic Habits11",
  "author": "James Clear11",
  "publishYear": 2020
}

### 2. Get All Books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/book

### 3. Get Book by ID (Change '1' to a real ID from the list above)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/book/1

### 4. Update a Book (Change '1' to a real ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/book/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Atomic Habits (Updated Edition)",
  "author": "James Clear",
  "publishYear": 2024
}

### 5. Delete a Book (Change '1' to a real ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/book/2

